1> create an ec2 instance and take its ssh
2> update the sshd_config file
# cd /etc/ssh
#vi sshd_config
3>update the following lines in above config files
PasswordAuthentication yes
PermitRootLogin yes
4> restart the ssh service
# sudo service sshd restart
5>create an user and assign it a password
#useradd chhaya
#passwd chhaya
6> take a new session in mobaxterm add credentials i.e username and password and login into session
7>it will ask for username and password for login 
